"{\"uid\": \"publicist24.com-france-considers-cancelling-olympic-opening-ceremony-amid-heightened-terror-threats\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Reports emerging from intelligence sources indicate that the French security service is deliberating over a pivotal decision-to enact \\\"plan B\\\" and cancel the much-anticipated opening ceremony of the Olympic Games  Security Concerns Mount Following Moscow Attack as France Braces for Olympic Games  In the wake of the recent terrorist atrocity that shookMoscow, France finds itself on high alert, grappling with the looming spectre of extremist violence as it prepares to host the prestigious Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 61, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.636122167108066, \"rank\": 0.43614488159035836, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9483705883511563, \"rank\": 0.03164616231261362, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9483705883511563, \"rank\": 0.03164616231261362, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6022222846915883e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The shadow of terror casts a pall over the grandeur of the event, prompting French authorities to contemplate drastic measures to safeguard against potential coordinated attacks.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.636122167108066, \"rank\": 0.43614488159035836, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reports emerging from intelligence sources indicate that the French security service is deliberating over a pivotal decision-to enact \\\"plan B\\\" and cancel the much-anticipated opening ceremony of theOlympic Games.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.636122167108066, \"rank\": 0.43614488159035836, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Citing concerns over the vulnerability of the event, particularly the planned river parade on the Seine, officials are wary of the potential risks posed by maintaining the ceremony in its current format.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.037451846773563e-15, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The heightened state of alert follows swiftly on the heels of a brutal terrorist assault at Crocus City Hall, an act of carnage that left a staggering death toll and sent shockwaves reverberating throughout the nation.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The attack, perpetrated by armed assailants who callously opened fire on concertgoers before setting the venue ablaze, stands as a stark reminder of the ever-present threat of extremism.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French President Emmanuel Macron wasted no time in responding to the barbaric act, swiftly convening the Defence and National Security Council to address the escalating crisis.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1540, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_Security_Council\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1071917670354906e-17, \"text\": \"Security Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_Security_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations_Security_Council\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the terrorist threat level elevated to its highest echelon, the government has pledged to deploy a formidable contingent of up to 20,000 military personnel tasked with ensuring the safety and security of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The tragedy at Crocus City Hall, which unfolded on the fateful evening of March 22nd, continues to haunt the collective consciousness of the nation, with the death toll climbing to a staggering 140 souls lost in the senseless violence.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the aftermath of the heinous act, authorities wasted no time in apprehending suspected perpetrators, with eight individuals detained in connection to the terrorist assault.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As France braces for the impending spectacle of the Olympic Games, the spectre of terrorism looms large, casting a pall over the festivities and prompting soul-searching conversations among officials tasked with safeguarding the event.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2348, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9483705883511563, \"rank\": 0.03164616231261362, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The delicate balance between preserving the spirit of celebration and ensuring the safety of participants and spectators alike hangs in the balance as the nation grapples with the sobering reality of an ever-evolving security landscape.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the eyes of the world poised to turn towards Paris this summer, the fate of the Olympic opening ceremony remains uncertain as French authorities weigh the imperatives of security against the backdrop of heightened terror threats.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 3054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2870, \"end\": 2875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6022222846915883e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2951, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.636122167108066, \"rank\": 0.43614488159035836, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a climate fraught with uncertainty and apprehension, the resilience of the human spirit stands as a beacon of hope as France vows to confront the spectre of extremism with unwavering resolve and solidarity.\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3177, \"end\": 3183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9483705883511563, \"rank\": 0.03164616231261362, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This article was created using automation and was thoroughly edited and fact-checked by one of our editorial staff members  Latest News from Europeyou needin your life  Copyright \\u00a9 Publicist 24.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Publicist 24 is built using thePure Journalismfor our readers.\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"https://ledvega.net/shop/  https://advertising.edu.vn/wp-includes/casino/  https://automation.edu.vn/wp-includes/casino/  https://thethaispabodakdev.in/wp-includes/buangsial/  https://noithatdepdanang.vn/products/  https://wishmarathi.com/wish/BH/  https://royalcollegedombivli.com/products/  https://thirdage.com/wp-content/products/  https://www.gurunanakschools.edu.in/products/  https://mikdental.in/wp-includes/js/ios/  https://kptripathi.co.in/wp-includes/css/cipeli/  https://www.varicoseveinlaser.in/location/wp-includes/js/jquery/ai/  https://wahe.co.in/cache/  https://vatans.com/dante/  https://www.sscnet.edu.bd/cache/  https://janjagrannews.com/cache/  https://mietjmu.in/cache/bonus41-bonus51/  https://cspbankmitrabc.co.in/wp-includes/css/cache/  https://estreianatv.com.br/jeetbuzz  https://giaotieptienganh.com.vn/wp-includes/js/jquery/cache/  https://tuyenmai.com/wp-includes/js/jquery/cache/  https://hindihelpme.com/wp-includes/css/bar/  https://smarteshop.pk/cache.php 